detail.name: Vegeta's Battle Armor
detail.effect: [Activate Main] Choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards and reduce its cost by 1 for the turn. Then, if your Leader has <Vegeta> in its card name, draw 1 card.

detail.name: ベジータの戦闘服
detail.effect: 【起動 メイン】相手のバトルカード1枚までを選び、このターン中、コスト-1。その後、自分のリーダーがカード名に「ベジータ」を含む場合、カード1枚を引く。
